# 7. AWS Setup Required

Terraform needs AWS credentials.

Install AWS CLI

sudo apt install awscli -y

Configure AWS

aws configure

Enter:

AWS Access Key
AWS Secret Key
Region (example: ap-south-1)

Test connection

aws sts get-caller-identity

